  <b>Instructions</b>
  <ul><li>Press Speak to begin speech recognition and Stop to end speech recognition.</li>
      <li>Say "color _____" to change the color of the circle. For example "color blue" to make the circle blue.</li>
      <li>Say "background _____" to change the background color of the canvas. For example "background yellow" to make the background yellow.</li>
      <li>Say "size _____" to change the size of the circle. For example "size 50" to make the circle with a diameter of 50.</li>
      <li>Say "help" to get help.</li>
      <li>Say "about" to learn about the program.</li>
      <li>If an incorrect color is detected, the background will go white or the circle will go black depending on which you are modifying.</li>
      <li>If an incorrect size is detected, you will be notified.</li>
    </ul>
